<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَلَا يَحْسَبَنَّ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا سَبَقُوا , إِنَّهُمْ لَا يُعْجِزُونَ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٢١:</span> <span class="c3">{سَبَقُوا}</span>: فَاتُوا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{لَا يُعْجِزُونَ}</span>: لَا يَفُوتُونَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الأنفال: ٥٩]</p> </div>